# Storyline, Backstory and Character Stats

Title: Encantadia: Origin of the Gems (Tentative: Subject to change)

Storyline:
Peace in Encantadia was never meant to last.
After the fall of the previous conflict, the elemental Brilyantes began to resonate with an unfamiliar pulse—one that echoed loss rather than power. The Goddesses Jelian and Joygen, guardians of whispers and flame, vanished without a trace. In their absence, the balance of the realms fractured.
The skies grew unstable. The oceans lost their rhythm. The land cracked with unrest.
Sensing a greater catastrophe, the Sang’gres—Amihan, Alena, Danaya, and Perina—reunited with the ancient guardians Dirk and Mary. Their journey revealed a forbidden truth: Jelian and Joygen were imprisoned within a sealed dimension known as the Gem Void, a realm born from corrupted Brilyante energy.
To rescue them, two new warriors rise—beings born not of divinity, but of sacrifice—chosen by the Gems themselves.
Now bound by fate, the eight must venture into collapsing realms, confront twisted elemental manifestations, and restore balance before Encantadia is consumed by its own power.


