Born of the northern winds and nurtured by the whispers of the sky, Dea commands the currents with precision and foresight. Calm and observant, she senses disturbances across the realms long before they manifest. The disappearance of Jelian weighs heavily on her, as the winds now carry only silence where once they carried guidance.

