Flamara (Fire)
Gifted with flames born from starlit embers, Flamara’s fire burns with a fierce, unyielding passion. The absence of Joygen dims the brilliance of her power, yet it strengthens her resolve to rescue the goddess who once taught her the true mastery of fire.

